movie.title: Fall Out Boy: Live from UCF Arena
movie.title_english: Fall Out Boy: Live from UCF Arena
movie.title_long: Fall Out Boy: Live from UCF Arena (2007)
movie.description_intro: The American rockers Fall Out Boy surely know how to rock. This live UCF Arena performance is no exception. The band performs hits like "Sugar, We're Goin Down," "Thnks fr th Mmrs," and many more.

movies.title: Waterworld
movies.summary: The polar ice caps have melted, and the earth is covered by water. The remaining people travel the seas, in search of survival. Several different societies exist. The Mariner falls from his customary and solitary existence into having to care for a woman and a young girl while being pursued by the evil forces of the Deacon.

movies.title: Night Train to Lisbon
movies.summary: This movie is about aging Swiss Professor Raimund Gregorius (Jeremy Irons) of classical languages who, after a chance encounter with a Portuguese woman, quits his job and travels to Lisbon in the hope of discovering the fate of a certain author, a doctor and poet who fought against Portuguese Dictator Antonio de Oliveira Salazar.

movies.title: Touching the Void
movies.summary: In 1985 two friends, Joe Simpson and Simon Yates, set out to climb Siula Grande in Peru via the West Face, a hitherto unaccomplished feat by any climber. After a tough ascent they succeed but on the descent they run into significant problems. Soon they are both in dire danger and the chances of surviving are slim.

movies.title: Indie Game: The Movie
movies.summary: A documentary that follows the journeys of indie game developers as they create games and release those works, and themselves, to the world.
